	<article id="post-3406" class="post-3406 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-specials category-workshops tag-2012-tour tag-statistics tag-travel">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2012/09/21/5-weeks-3-the-stats/" rel="bookmark">5 Weeks (3): The Stats</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2012/09/21/5-weeks-3-the-stats/" title="5:30 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-09-21T17:30:57+00:00">September 21, 2012</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/author/chris/" title="View all posts by Chris Marquardt" rel="author">Chris Marquardt</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2012/09/21/5-weeks-3-the-stats/#comments" title="Comment on 5 Weeks (3): The Stats"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="3406 http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?p=3406">2</span></a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p class="wp-flattr-button"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?flattrss_redirect&amp;id=3406&amp;md5=3b9accd115969e50cde1ba1e4b223fea" title="Flattr" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/plugins/flattr/img/flattr-badge-large.png" alt="flattr this!"/></a></p><p><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/Photo-5D56AFD6-A35B-4CFA-BE1B-9E4EB04A0913-20120815-111229-512.jpg" alt="Airplane" title="Photo-5D56AFD6-A35B-4CFA-BE1B-9E4EB04A0913-20120815-111229-512.jpg" border="0" width="512" height="384" /></p>
<p>A quick detour in the 2012 North Amercian Tour recap.. You know I&#8217;m curious, so I&#8217;ve just put together some stats about the tour.</p>
<p>During the five weeks, I&#8217;ve been flying on 13 different airplanes (must have added at least another 100 hot pixels to my camera&#8217;s sensor, talk about <a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/2012/04/26/tfttf545-cosmic-particles/">cosmic radiation and cameras</a>), I have visited 6 different cities (not including the layovers), slept in 9 different hotels or other accommodations (including couches) and have driven 7 different rental cars.</p>
<p>*phew* … I&#8217;ll need a tour manager soon</p>
<p>&raquo; <a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/tag/2012-Tour/">more from the 2012 tour</a></p>
