<p>Tips from the Top Floor is a <strong>weekly show</strong> about photography. It is brought to you by photographic mythbuster Chris Marquardt. When he's not on a commercial assignment, Chris brings his <strong>workshops</strong> to Germany, the US, Canada, Japan and even the Himalayas. He is behind <strong>PocketChris</strong>, the photo instructor in your pocket. Watch Chris live all over the world, as the Photo Guy on the <strong>Tech Guy Radio Show</strong> with Leo Laporte.</p>
